Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}is the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... is the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, {\alpha&HFF&}I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... {\alpha&HFF&}just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.59,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(358,354)}Gamble
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when do you want him killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me to him, I'll kill him instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The earlier, the better. It could even be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it may be a little careless to decide straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I'll think carefully about when and how we should kill him, and I'll give you my answer after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. {\alpha&HFF&}No matter what happens, don't kill until I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. No matter what happens, don't kill until I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can promise you that... {\alpha&HFF&}with regard to L...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can promise you that... with regard to L...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, give me your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather slow on the uptake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me yours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that when you're part of a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, I'm being marked by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, they have the ability to bug specific telephone lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! In that case, have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa will give you one of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I started to use each for a different purpose, I ended up with three!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours should probably be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'll give you a love call every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And send you lots of texts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be leaving the phone switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you only when necessary, and ensure that information is kept to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... {\alpha&HFF&}when will you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... when will you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether we go ahead with killing L or not, I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like the call is going to be very romantic, but if we can talk love afterwards, I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Misa, you'd better go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?! It's only 7pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for lovers has only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go grab something to eat together, and follow that by watching the sun set, and then it'll be time to get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For today, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when you talk to Rem outside, make sure no one is around, and do so quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do the same with Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san! Please come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty surprised when you just kissed her out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's necessary to ensure that Misa falls utterly in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I need to decide whether or not to kill L tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ryuuga's identity as L isn't publicly known, I've got to be prepared for the fact that if he dies, I will be strongly suspected of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that since you declared yourselves to be friends, you might be having second thoughts about killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friends"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went along with what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning I've said, "if he wants friendship, I'll take it".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Yagami Light, Ryuuga is merely a friend for appearance's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is Kira's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. L is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's revealed himself to me as L, I'll have to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make it an "accidental death", hardly anyone will suspect that I'm Kira, and even if they do, there'll be no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine what will happen after L dies... {\alpha&HFF&}this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine what will happen after L dies... this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, L... {\alpha&HFF&}or rather Ryuuzaki or Ryuuga, will be your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, L... or rather Ryuuzaki or Ryuuga, will be your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumbs from snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die in the next few days, your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Where's this suddenly coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange it so that you can use Watari as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest will be up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:05:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! You said that the majority of your suspicions had already been dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How deeply do you really suspect my son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I really understand what I truly think myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like this has ever happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira and the second Kira have indeed made contact... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm in a dire pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira and the second Kira have indeed made contact... I'm in a dire pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, right now, I'm probably incapable of calmly analyzing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be doing this solely because I have no other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, {\alpha&HFF&}if I am killed now, please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, if I am killed now, {\alpha&HFF&}please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, if I am killed now, please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make another surprise attack, but it can't be helped... {\alpha&HFF&}this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make another surprise attack, but it can't be helped... this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, I'm just pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-kun... hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yagami-kun... hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I'd like to speak to him alone for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure this is okay? What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. You said you were "scared of showing your face in public", are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I realized I'd be fine as long as you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside, you're the only one who knows I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... {\alpha&HFF&}you are Kira. I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... you are Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... you are Kira. I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yourself that it's lonely without me around, {\alpha&HFF&}so I thought I'd come in for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yourself that it's lonely without me around, so I thought I'd come in for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I don't die, university is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're not around, there's no one I can talk to at my level. {\alpha&HFF&}It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're not around, there's no one I can talk to at my level. It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus the talented Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really be safe to kill him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, by non-chalantly turning up like this, he's just trying to break my will to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably trying to warn me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just what he wants to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we grab some cake from the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got no lectures next period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have shortcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a shoot nearby, so I thought I'd drop by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, one of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's wonderfully unique, isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wait... I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa can see Ryuuga's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Light's girlfriend, Amane Misa. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuuga Hideki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's got the same name as the idol. Funny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that's different from the name I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}this time, your decision to come out has worked against y--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, this time, your decision to come out has worked against y--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, he's realized?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he thinks there's a possibility that she's the second Kira, surely he wouldn't be able to laugh like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I'm very jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a fan of Misa's since the August edition of "Eighteen".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Really?! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, it's Misa-Misa, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It is Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Misa-Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always seem to get noticed when there's lots of young people around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I buy your stuff every month!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Someone just touched my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nerve! To take advantage of all this confusion to do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga-san, you're so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna feel too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out L's real name from Misa as soon as possible, but with all these people around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! {\alpha&HFF&}It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be late, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Misa leaves, all I need to do is make one phone call to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye Light! See you after work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we go, Yagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead, I need to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been all sorts of fun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to find out your real name and kill you myself.
Comment: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been all sorts of fun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to find out your real name and kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like someone dropped this phone amid all the confusion just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Misa's phone. I'll return it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}you may think you've outwitted me, but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, you may think you've outwitted me, {\alpha&HFF&}but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, you may think you've outwitted me, but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I ring that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that right. We've done it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably both good and bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended Amane Misa on suspicion of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has he suspected Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she was caught so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the second Kira sent the video tapes from Amane's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they left a great deal of evidence, such as hairs and clothing fibres, stuck to packing tape used to seal the envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that announcing she's under suspicion of being the second Kira would cause public chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're saying she's gone to be questioned about the charges held against her manager for drug possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I doubt the public will find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those videos... {\alpha&HFF&}I should have ensure I destroyed the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those videos... I should have ensure I destroyed the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, by being around me, rather than hiding, Ryuuga managed to protect himself, and get right to the heart of the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gamble... I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight has just begun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, has she said anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a visual of her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been apprehended on suspicion of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to take these precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that there was enough evidence in Amane's room to assure us that she's the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, {\alpha&HFF&}if she knows Kira, and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, if she knows Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, if she knows Kira, and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as you're careful, I won't mind if you use slightly dubious methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, as long as you're careful, I won't mind if you use slightly dubious methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her to spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}please prepare yourself for the fact that I'll be bringing Light-kun in for questioning regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Yagami-san, please prepare yourself for the fact that I'll be bringing Light-kun in for questioning regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Amane has said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Amane has said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and bring up a visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! After three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! {\alpha&HFF&}Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might have been too much for a girl who's only around twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be her limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... {\alpha&HFF&}hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that you admit you are the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}I don't know anything about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't know anything about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore... {\alpha&HFF&}I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore... I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you could kill me in an instant if you wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you want me to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't endure this anymore, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill you, I'll kill Yagami Light too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all his faul--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you're really willing to die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! {\alpha&HFF&}If you won't kill me I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! If you won't kill me I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari! Don't let her bite her tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, she's not being manipulated by Kira just before she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rem, {\alpha&HFF&}what do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rem, what do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}even though I offered to help Misa escape, she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, even though I offered to help Misa escape, she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because she realized that she would be seen as having special powers, which would cause you trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she realized she was reaching the limits of her mentality, {\alpha&HFF&}she began to ask for me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she realized she was reaching the limits of her mentality, she began to ask for me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this, {\alpha&HFF&}because she wants to be loved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this, because she wants to be loved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she begged me to, there's no way I could kill Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to watch her suffer like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forfeiting ownership of the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you forfeit ownership of a Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}all the memories you have of it disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you forfeit ownership of a Death Note, all the memories you have of it disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would forget about all the people she's killed, {\alpha&HFF&}and the fact that Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would forget about all the people she's killed, and the fact that Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there would be no danger of her giving away your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she would no longer be able to see Ryuk or myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.10,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(358,389)}A few hours earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}this means that you'll forget everything you know about Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, this means that you'll forget everything you know about Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human you love is Yagami Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Those feelings alone will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human you love is Yagami Light. Those feelings alone will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you should give up ownership of your Death Note and entrust everything to Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is no longer the owner of a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that that was our sole option.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa has no memory of the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}it's possible that she can be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa has no memory of the Death Note, it's possible that she can be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}I knew that this would be the best option for you, which is why I suggested it to Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, I knew that this would be the best option for you, {\alpha&HFF&}which is why I suggested it to Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, I knew that this would be the best option for you, which is why I suggested it to Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't save Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't save Misa, I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a fair idea of what L might do from here, {\alpha&HFF&}and I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a fair idea of what L might do from here, and I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,298)}To be continued
